  "commit_message": "chore: reduce memory pressure in run-app-component-tests-chrome (#33971)\n\n* fix(frontend-shared): drop eager Shiki init from CT support\n\nEach spec page-load in experimentalSingleTabRunMode reuses the renderer\nprocess, and Blink's per-realm DOM constructor cache (anchored in V8's\nEternal handles) prevents prior page realms from being fully released.\nAnything anchored in a retained realm stays alive too — and the eager\n`await initHighlighter()` was anchoring 150 MB of reserved Onigasm WASM\nmemory ",
